    "\n",
    "\n",
    "We apply a physical sanity filter:\n",
    "\n",
    "- Use r-band only  \n",
    "- Respect published upper limits  \n",
    "- After 8 days, any point brighter than 20.5 mag is treated as an upper limit  \n",
    "\n",
    "This prevents artificial late-time rebrightening.\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
